<%= provide(:title, "Strength") %>

<h1 class = "center">What is Strength?</h1>
<p>
	Some bricks are stronger than others. Stronger bricks can survive at higher altitudes due to
  <span class="overlap" data-text = "blessings">stronger clay</span>.
</p>

<p>
	When you put a brick on top of a brick that matches it's color or put two bricks of the same color
  on the same place at the same time, you get a stronger brick. A brick's strength is shown in how many
  lines it has on it.
</p>

<p>
	When you put a brick on top of a brick of a different color or put two bricks of different colors on
  the tower at the same time, you get a weaker brick. If a brick's strength falls below zero, it is
   destroyed.
</p>